OL,3,CBrighton manager Roberto De Zerbi to
OL,4,Cleave the club by 'mutual agreement'
OL,6,FBrighton and Hove Albion's head coach
OL,7,FRoberto De Zerbi will leave the club
OL,8,Fafter tomorrow's final Premier League
OL,9,Fmatch of the season against Manchester
OL,10,FUnited.
OL,12,FDe Zerbi, joined the Seagulls in
OL,13,FSeptember 2022, following the
OL,14,Fdeparture of Graham Potter to Chelsea.
OL,16,FUnder his leadership, the club has
OL,17,Fseen highest top flight finish in 2022/
OL,18,F23 and went down to last 16 of the
OL,19,FUEFA Europa League.
