OL,3,CBrighton manager Roberto De Zerbi to
OL,4,Cleave the club by 'mutual agreement'
OL,6,F"We have mutually agreed to end
OL,7,FRoberto's contract at a time that
OL,8,Fsuits both parties allowing us the
OL,9,Fearliest opportunity to plan for next
OL,10,Fseason, and Roberto plenty of time to
OL,11,Fconsider his next move and his future.
OL,13,F"I am sure our fans will give Roberto
OL,14,Fand his staff a wonderful and fully
OL,15,Fdeserved send off at the Amex before,
OL,16,Fduring and after tomorrow's match.
